    <entry>
      <title>评价类模型</title>
      <link href="/2023/01/13/%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E7%B1%BB%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B/"/>
      <url>/2023/01/13/%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E7%B1%BB%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="层次分析法（AHP）"><a href="#层次分析法（AHP）" class="headerlink" title="层次分析法（AHP）"></a>层次分析法（AHP）</h1><p>&emsp;&emsp;<strong>原理：将与决策有关的因素分解成目标层、准则层、方案层等若干层次，通过对各因素的计算和比较，得出不同因素的权重，为决策者选择最优方案提供参考依据</strong></p><h2 id="建立层次结构模型"><a href="#建立层次结构模型" class="headerlink" title="建立层次结构模型"></a>建立层次结构模型</h2><p>&emsp;&emsp;将决策问题分解为三个层次，最上层为目标层O，即()；最下层为方案层P，即()；中间层为准则层C，包括()<br><strong>注：用亿图绘制，连线时可能出现跳线，单击鼠标右键，将“显示跳线样式”去掉</strong><br>   <img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/01/15/YbrvCVExJjFd5gi.jpg" alt="层次分析法1.jpg"></p><ol><li>目标层为评价目标，即评价对象中分最高的</li><li>方案层评价对象，题目中给出</li><li>准则层为指标，通过它来评价好坏，指标有的是题目中背景材料给出，有的需要根据自己常识，或查找<a href="https://search.chongbuluo.com/">相关资料</a>，筛选出最合适的指标</li><li>总的来说，方案层为目标层服务，具体选评价对象中的哪一个，则需要通过准则层进行确定</li></ol><h2 id="构造两两判断矩阵"><a href="#构造两两判断矩阵" class="headerlink" title="构造两两判断矩阵"></a>构造两两判断矩阵</h2><p>&emsp;&emsp;判断矩阵O-C<br><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/01/15/54Uyn6u9TtdJqjS.jpg" alt="层次分析法3.jpg"><br>&emsp;&emsp;判断矩阵C-P<br><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/01/15/JmK5utHPYfWXz3s.jpg" alt="层次分析法2.jpg"><br>表中数据一般为通过<a href="https://search.chongbuluo.com/">查找相关资料</a>，自己填写<br><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/01/15/VfKMW3S56XsItR8.jpg" alt="层次分析法4.jpg"></p><h2 id="一致性检验"><a href="#一致性检验" class="headerlink" title="一致性检验"></a>一致性检验</h2><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/01/15/8Nva5YcUKkzQLqh.jpg" alt="层次分析法5.jpg"><br><strong>注：λmax为矩阵的最大特征值，每个判断矩阵都要求最大特征值，并进行一致性检验，若不满足一致性检验，则需要对数据进行调整，朝各行（各列）满足成倍数关系的方向调整</strong></p><h2 id="计算各指标权重W"><a href="#计算各指标权重W" class="headerlink" title="计算各指标权重W"></a>计算各指标权重W</h2><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">disp</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;请输入判断矩阵A： &#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="算数平均法"><a href="#算数平均法" class="headerlink" title="算数平均法"></a>算数平均法</h3><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">% 第一步：将判断矩阵按照列归一化（每一个元素除以其所在列的和）</span></span><br><span class="line">SUM = sum(A) <span class="comment">%按列求和，得到一个行向量</span></span><br><span class="line">n = <span class="built_in">size</span>(A,<span class="number">1</span>)<span class="comment">% 求得矩阵的行数（列数）注：判断矩阵A是一个方阵，所以r和c相同，可以用同一个字母n表示</span></span><br><span class="line">S = <span class="built_in">repmat</span>(SUM,n,<span class="number">1</span>) <span class="comment">%将行向量SUM扩展为与A相同阶数的矩阵S</span></span><br><span class="line">Stand_A = A ./ S  <span class="comment">% 将两个矩阵对应的元素相除</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">% 第二步：将归一化的矩阵按行求和，得到列向量</span></span><br><span class="line">sum(Stand_A,<span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">% 第三步：将相加后得到的向量中每个元素除以n即可得到权重向量</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">disp</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;算术平均法求权重的结果为：&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">disp</span>(sum(Stand_A,<span class="number">2</span>) / n)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="几何平均法"><a href="#几何平均法" class="headerlink" title="几何平均法"></a>几何平均法</h3><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">% 第一步：将A的元素按照行相乘得到一个新的列向量</span></span><br><span class="line">Prduct_A = prod(A,<span class="number">2</span>)<span class="comment">% prod函数和sum函数类似，一个用于乘，一个用于加  dim = 2 维度是行</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">% 第二步：将新的向量的每个分量开n次方</span></span><br><span class="line">Prduct_n_A = Prduct_A .^ (<span class="number">1</span>/n)<span class="comment">% 对每个元素进行乘方操作，因此要加.号。  ^符号表示乘方哦  开n次方，等价于求1/n次方</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">% 第三步：对该列向量进行归一化即可得到权重向量</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">% 将这个列向量中的每一个元素除以这一个向量的和即可</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">disp</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;几何平均法求权重的结果为：&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">disp</span>(Prduct_n_A ./ sum(Prduct_n_A))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="特征值法"><a href="#特征值法" class="headerlink" title="特征值法"></a>特征值法</h3><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">% 第一步：求出矩阵A的最大特征值以及其对应的特征向量</span></span><br><span class="line">[V,D] = eig(A)    <span class="comment">%V是特征向量, D是由特征值构成的对角矩阵（除了对角线元素外，其余位置元素全为0）</span></span><br><span class="line">Max_eig = <span class="built_in">max</span>(D(:)) <span class="comment">%取D中全部元素，拼成一个列向量，找到其中的最大值</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">% 用矩阵与常数的大小判断运算找到最大特征值所在位置</span></span><br><span class="line">D == Max_eig <span class="comment">%进行判断，返回同阶矩阵，且只有D中元素为Max_eig的值为1，其他元素都变为0</span></span><br><span class="line">[r,c] = <span class="built_in">find</span>(D == Max_eig , <span class="number">1</span>)<span class="comment">% 找到D中第一个与最大特征值相等的元素的位置，记录它的行和列。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">% 第二步：对求出的特征向量进行归一化即可得到我们的权重</span></span><br><span class="line">V(:,c)<span class="comment">%根据上面找到的最大特征值的列数c找到对应的特征向量</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">disp</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;特征值法求权重的结果为：&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">disp</span>( V(:,c) ./ sum(V(:,c)) )<span class="comment">%标准化</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="根据权重矩阵计算得分，并进行排序"><a href="#根据权重矩阵计算得分，并进行排序" class="headerlink" title="根据权重矩阵计算得分，并进行排序"></a>根据权重矩阵计算得分，并进行排序</h2><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/01/15/lqRhHWgnL23sPwK.jpg" alt="层次分析法6.jpg"><br>&emsp;&emsp;<strong>注：指标的权重由O-C判断矩阵确定，不同方案在对应指标的权重由C-P判断矩阵确定。对每个方案，用指标的权重x方案在该指标下的权重并进行求和，即可得到分数</strong></p><h2 id="局限性"><a href="#局限性" class="headerlink" title="局限性"></a>局限性</h2><p>&emsp;&emsp;评价的绝策层（指标）不能太多，太多的话n会很大，判断矩阵和一致矩阵差异可能会很大<br>&emsp;&emsp;指标的数据是已知的，且判断矩阵可能不满足一致性检验，这时需要用TOPSIS法<br>&emsp;&emsp;<strong>注：一般来说，评价类模型就是将层次分析法中计算指标权重的方法与TOPSIS法相结合</strong></p><h1 id="TOPSIS法（优劣解距离法）"><a href="#TOPSIS法（优劣解距离法）" class="headerlink" title="TOPSIS法（优劣解距离法）"></a>TOPSIS法（优劣解距离法）</h1><h2 id="确定指标权重"><a href="#确定指标权重" class="headerlink" title="确定指标权重"></a>确定指标权重</h2><ul><li>层次分析法（主观赋值）</li><li>熵权法（客观赋值）</li></ul><h2 id="将原始矩阵正向化"><a href="#将原始矩阵正向化" class="headerlink" title="将原始矩阵正向化"></a>将原始矩阵正向化</h2><p>&emsp;&emsp;<strong>注：一般来说，原始矩阵第0列为评价对象，第0行为指标</strong><br><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/01/16/9EZxv3iFscXB8QO.png" alt="TOPSIS法2.png"><br>&emsp;&emsp;<strong>原理：将所有的指标类型统一转化为极大型指标</strong><br><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/01/16/QPpNhtY85VioZSU.png" alt="TOPSIS法1.png"></p><ol><li>极小型指标<br> 公式：max-x <figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">%%将极小型指标的转换用定义的Min2Max函数来求，并放在Min2Max.m文件中</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="params">[posit_x]</span> = <span class="title">Min2Max</span><span class="params">(x)</span></span></span><br><span class="line">posit_x = <span class="built_in">max</span>(x) - x;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>中间型指标<br> 公式：<br> <img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/01/16/aiktQncHJoPmw7Z.png" alt="TOPSIS3.png"> <figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="params">[posit_x]</span> = <span class="title">Mid2Max</span><span class="params">(x,best)</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    M = <span class="built_in">max</span>(<span class="built_in">abs</span>(x-best));</span><br><span class="line">   posit_x = <span class="number">1</span> - <span class="built_in">abs</span>(x-best) / M;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>区间型指标<br> <img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/01/16/uFyB4wYxamlMEc5.png" alt="TOPSIS4.png"> <figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="params">[posit_x]</span> = <span class="title">Inter2Max</span><span class="params">(x,a,b)</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    r_x = <span class="built_in">size</span>(X,<span class="number">1</span>);  <span class="comment">% 求X的行数，即对象的个数</span></span><br><span class="line">    M = <span class="built_in">max</span>([a-<span class="built_in">min</span>(x),<span class="built_in">max</span>(x)-b]);</span><br><span class="line">   posit_x = <span class="built_in">zeros</span>(r_x,<span class="number">1</span>); <span class="comment">% 初始化posit_x全为0 ，初始化的目的是节省处理时间</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">for</span> <span class="built_in">i</span> = <span class="number">1</span>: r_x</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">if</span> x(<span class="built_in">i</span>) &lt; a</span><br><span class="line">         posit_x(<span class="built_in">i</span>) = <span class="number">1</span>-(a-x(<span class="built_in">i</span>))/M;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">elseif</span> x(<span class="built_in">i</span>) &gt; b</span><br><span class="line">         posit_x(<span class="built_in">i</span>) = <span class="number">1</span>-(x(<span class="built_in">i</span>)-b)/M;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">       posit_x(<span class="built_in">i</span>) = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">end</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">end</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="正向化矩阵标准化"><a href="#正向化矩阵标准化" class="headerlink" title="正向化矩阵标准化"></a>正向化矩阵标准化</h2><p>&emsp;&emsp;目的：消除不同指标量纲的影响<br>   <img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/01/16/jdsnOCYuo7NqyPX.png" alt="TOPSIS法5.png"><br>   <figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Z = X ./ <span class="built_in">repmat</span>(sum(X.*X) .^ <span class="number">0.5</span>, n, <span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">disp</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;标准化矩阵 Z = &#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">disp</span>(Z)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="计算得分并归一化"><a href="#计算得分并归一化" class="headerlink" title="计算得分并归一化"></a>计算得分并归一化</h2><p>&emsp;&emsp;公式：<br>   <img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/01/16/V8b4WFJMw6psnQv.png" alt="TOPSIS法6.png"><br>   <img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/01/16/1DA7rjKEcsG8JQx.png" alt="TOPSIS法7.png"><br>   <figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">D_P = sum([(Z - <span class="built_in">repmat</span>(<span class="built_in">max</span>(Z),n,<span class="number">1</span>)) .^ <span class="number">2</span> ],<span class="number">2</span>) .^ <span class="number">0.5</span>;   <span class="comment">% D+ 与最大值的距离向量</span></span><br><span class="line">D_N = sum([(Z - <span class="built_in">repmat</span>(<span class="built_in">min</span>(Z),n,<span class="number">1</span>)) .^ <span class="number">2</span> ],<span class="number">2</span>) .^ <span class="number">0.5</span>;   <span class="comment">% D- 与最小值的距离向量</span></span><br><span class="line">S = D_N ./ (D_P+D_N);    <span class="comment">% 未归一化的得分</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">disp</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;最后的得分为：&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">stand_S = S / sum(S)</span><br><span class="line">[sorted_S,index] = <span class="built_in">sort</span>(stand_S ,<span class="string">&#x27;descend&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>]]></content>
      
      
